### identity-service dev RSA keypair ###
# Generated at startup by RsaKeyPairProvider for local/dev JWT signing (see
# Archive/Architecture/ARCHITECTURE.md §4/§7). The private key must never
# leave identity-service, so it is never committed. The paired PUBLIC key at
# gateway/keys/identity-dev-public-key.pem IS committed on purpose — the Kong
# gateway work item reads it from that exact path.
identity-service/keys/
